            div(class="w-24 h-24 bg-dark-800/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6")
              svg(class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24")
                path(stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z")
            h3(class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4") Belum Ada Anime Complete
            p(class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-md mx-auto") Saat ini belum ada data anime complete yang tersedia. Silakan kembali lagi nanti untuk update terbaru.
            div(class="mt-8")
              a(href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-600 text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-accent-700 transition-all font-medium")
                svg(class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24")
                  path(stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6")
